# ─── Claude Code ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shared config (.claude/launch.json, settings.json) is committed on purpose;
# only personal per-machine overrides are ignored.
.claude/settings.local.json

# ─── Capacitor / native ──────────────────────────────────────────
# The native android/ and ios/ projects ARE committed on purpose, so you
# can customise icons, signing, Info.plist, etc. Their own .gitignore files
# (generated by `npx cap add`) already exclude the build artifacts —
# Pods/, .gradle/, build/, DerivedData/, local.properties, copied web
# assets, and generated capacitor.config.json.
#
# Prefer NOT to track the native projects and just regenerate them with
# `npx cap add`? Then uncomment these two lines:
# /android
# /ios
